descript.abstract: The Streets of the City and County of Denver, Colorado. This dataset is continually undergoing change as they occur within the city. To determine the last change made on a particular street, consult the Editdate field for the particular road segment.
descript.purpose: To digitally and accurately represent the streets of the City and County of Denver.

dataqual.logic: Streets have been digitized from the various sets of aerial photography that the City has acquired through the years. New Streets are also added from Public Works - Development Engineering Services (PWDES) Computer Aided Design (CAD) drawings.
dataqual.complete: All areas of new subdivisions are added, as new subdivisions are platted by PWDES the streets are added to the layer.
